le` and `walineLocale` for i18n config ![new](https://img.shields.io/badge/-new-brightgreen)\n\n---\n\n## 安装\n\n```bash\nnpm i vuepress-plugin-comment2@next\n```\n\n或\n\n```bash\nyarn add -D vuepress-plugin-comment2@next\n```\n\n## 特性\n\n- 页面信息组件\n- 支持 Waline\n\n## 从 V1 迁移\n\n名称从 `@mr-hope/vuepress-plugin-comment` 改为 `vuepress-plugin-comment2`. ⚠\n\n- Valine 服务已被移除 ![移除](https://img.shields.io/badge/-移除-red)\n\n  Valine 现已缺乏维护并可能泄露隐私. 你应当使用 [Waline](https://waline.js.org) 替代它.\n\n- Vssue 暂未适配 V2 ![警告](https://img.shields.io/badge/-警告-yellow)\n\n- 多分类支持 ![新增](https://img.shields.io/badge/-新增-brightgreen)\n\n- 选项 `hint` 控制悬停在页面信息上是否显示提示 ![新增](https://img.shields.io/badge/-新增-brightgreen)\n\n- 选项 `delay`，控制页面加载和切换后初始化评论服务的延迟 ![新增](https://img.shields.io/badge/-新增-brightgreen)\n\n- 选项 `pageInfoLocale` 和 `walineLocale` 用于国际化配置 ![新增](https://img.shields.io/badge/-新增-brightgreen)\n","readmeFilename":"README.md","_id":"vuepress-plugin-comment2@2.0.0-beta.25","_nodeVersion":"16.13.1","_npmVersion":"lerna/4.0.0/node@v16.13.1+x64 (win32)","dist":{"integrity":"sha512-XlNhb0soU3VnERV9ZQdEg9kNVz1bISP45XEUcXtcTUXSGmrYVg51B/43eDiBc+oABey8eboblY2jDI0wC25eGA==","shasum":"f5648b631da0aeca503a6a487c6cc113d59d0953","tarball":"https://registry.npmjs.org/vuepress-plugin-comment2/-/vuepress-plugin-comment2-2.0.0-beta.25.tgz","fileCount":46,"unpackedSize":53518,"npm-signature":"-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\r\nVersion: OpenPGP.js v4.10.10\r\nComment: https://openpgpjs.org\r\n\r\nwsFzBAEBCAAGBQJiO1peACEJED1NWxICdlZqFiEECWMYAoorWMhJKdjhPU1b\r\nEgJ2Vmo7JQ/+NLFEdyuLmTMm2sQ0IsFWyuFpJf0g6QPOs0pdj3Oxjz1UI0WY\r\nTKwrz3pS1pES8GsacvazanO0kEFIMOgQK+fHWtEUGy7DE7ohBv42nH5khAnm\r\nzYtxwLb55KSrqepuirL3QYJQqWheB181+qYJmisMOdvBM2LFN4dI40FVQnXM\r\nB0gdLPujXX7JCKVfmmPbEtZZh4UKBtN4USJnbVocCeYwBWCG8Ildp5w+CP1g\r\nkghMnUJxqSLfcv4DoVeVcRyWxvdr3xxdHPGZf0WnhX8fDUoWT+qRVb6nmYP1\r\n6BwgD8/VM1NqJ8RwFa7cTRpnSV++VzxXGtiqET8fS5yg6fKF/WKorLZPvVJR\r\ntBaNS62SsT4lxaErf1fqguZwNVQbSxwAO2Cqz9C8J4L8JSiFK/R3e0xY1wTE\r\nVrIhwwUVQ